text: IFK Göteborg is an association football club which plays in Sweden for Gothenburg. The club won the UEFA Cup in 1982 and 1987. The club also won the Swedish national championship in 1908, 1910, 1918, 1934–35, 1941–42, 1957–58, 1969, 1982, 1983, 1984, 1987, 1990, 1991, 1993, 1994, 1995, 1996 and 2007. ==References== == Other websites == * IFK Göteborg Category:Swedish football clubs Category:1904 establishments in Sweden Category:Sport in Gothenburg
